<p>
	<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: small; text-align: justify; text-indent: 35px;">Art. 7&ordm; S&atilde;o direitos do advogado:</span></p>
<p>
	.................</p>
<p align="justify">
	&sect; 2&ordm;-B. Poder&aacute; o advogado realizar a sustenta&ccedil;&atilde;o oral no recurso interposto contra a decis&atilde;o monocr&aacute;tica de relator que julgar o m&eacute;rito ou n&atilde;o conhecer dos seguintes recursos ou a&ccedil;&otilde;es:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://www.planalto.gov.br/ccivil_03/_Ato2019-2022/2022/Lei/L14365.htm#art2">(Inclu&iacute;do pela Lei n&ordm; 14.365, de 2022)</a></p>
<p align="justify">
	I - recurso de apela&ccedil;&atilde;o;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://www.planalto.gov.br/ccivil_03/_Ato2019-2022/2022/Lei/L14365.htm#art2">(Inclu&iacute;do pela Lei n&ordm; 14.365, de 2022)</a></p>
<p align="justify">
	II - recurso ordin&aacute;rio;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://www.planalto.gov.br/ccivil_03/_Ato2019-2022/2022/Lei/L14365.htm#art2">(Inclu&iacute;do pela Lei n&ordm; 14.365, de 2022)</a></p>
<p align="justify">
	III - recurso especial;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://www.planalto.gov.br/ccivil_03/_Ato2019-2022/2022/Lei/L14365.htm#art2">(Inclu&iacute;do pela Lei n&ordm; 14.365, de 2022)</a></p>
<p align="justify">
	IV - recurso extraordin&aacute;rio;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://www.planalto.gov.br/ccivil_03/_Ato2019-2022/2022/Lei/L14365.htm#art2">(Inclu&iacute;do pela Lei n&ordm; 14.365, de 2022)</a></p>
<p align="justify">
	V - embargos de diverg&ecirc;ncia;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://www.planalto.gov.br/ccivil_03/_Ato2019-2022/2022/Lei/L14365.htm#art2">(Inclu&iacute;do pela Lei n&ordm; 14.365, de 2022)</a></p>
<p align="justify">
	VI - a&ccedil;&atilde;o rescis&oacute;ria, mandado de seguran&ccedil;a, reclama&ccedil;&atilde;o, habeas corpus e outras a&ccedil;&otilde;es de compet&ecirc;ncia origin&aacute;ria.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://www.planalto.gov.br/ccivil_03/_Ato2019-2022/2022/Lei/L14365.htm#art2">(Inclu&iacute;do pela Lei n&ordm; 14.365, de 2022)</a></p>
